                    <head>
                        <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                    </head>
                    <p>The United Nations Security Council met from 3 to 6:30 p. m. on November 16
                        with debate continuing on the draft six-power resolution. No voting action
                        was taken. For the record, see U.N. document S/PV.523.</p>
